# Trust management
# 1. cn=adtrust agents,cn=sysaccounts,cn=etc,$SUFFIX can manage trusts, to allow modification via CIFS
# 2. cn=trust admins,cn=groups,cn=accounts,$SUFFIX can manage trusts (via ipa tools)
dn: cn=trusts,$SUFFIX
